{"tid":2374611,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［回復白滑］武漢肺炎間接令我生少咗好多暗瘡","createTime":"2021-01-21T10:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T00:28:00.000Z","uid":171902,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a5aefd12a7b7fcfc64fbfc224247b224d67636","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹自大學開始一直受暗瘡困擾，已有數年。自武漢肺炎爆發，美容院關閉，我有大半年無做facial 無做針清，但神奇地生少咗好多暗瘡，之前生襯一爆就額頭+兩頰，而家基本上淨係額頭間中會有，兩頰都冇乜點生。呢半年我都做咗唔少護膚清潔上嘅改變，想整好啲皮膚，以下綜合咗幾樣，我認為係對暗瘡治療有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅皮膚狀態：T字位會比較多油，生嘅暗瘡有時石頭瘡，但大部分都係生啲有癑，細細粒令人好想唧個種。生來生去都生喺舊個啲位。如果有人同我都係咁，我建議你睇埋落去。<br />\nBtw 我用個啲野全完都勁平，無錢但又想take care 皮膚狀況嘅人都可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好唧佢<br />\n針清、自己用針唧、用棉花棒唧都唔好做，咁樣會令到有好多傷口更易發炎。等到佢熟，洗面嘅時候佢就會自然爆，到時再搽茶樹gel。我諗返之前發現我針清完一個星期係會好啲，但第二個星期就多數會又生返，沒完沒了。<br />\n<br />\n2. 用咩清潔<br />\n唔化妝時就早晚用清水清潔。化咗妝要落妝，為咗要確保乾淨，我眼嘴個啲位會用Bioderma 粉紅色卸妝水，面就會用油，大家聽到油可能會好驚，我用緊shu uemura 綠色個隻洗完好乾淨乾爽就唔會lup痴痴。沖完涼之後，我會用innisfree 綠色個隻洗面，洗面嗰陣盡量細力啲，最後過水用按壓嘅方法，減少對皮膚嘅刺激，正常洗完面塊面唔應該紅。<br />\n<br />\n3. 用咩搽暗瘡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQVdwDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQVdwDG.png&h=c443de65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搽嘅時候記得，記得，記得，每搽一粒暗瘡都要用新一邊嘅棉花棒，唔好搽完一粒又一粒。呢枝野勁平，好似30蚊一枝。gel又勁清爽，個人感覺佢幾好。<br />\n<br />\n4. 用咩護膚品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yqdwD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yqdwD3.png&h=7ddf3e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKfQySo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKfQySo.png&h=1c6540de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爽膚水我仲會用薏仁爽膚水，好平勁大枝，洗完面就倒落化妝棉成塊面敷五分鐘。個枝陶土就淨係敷喺暗瘡上面。保濕我都係亂咁揀，保濕就好了<br />\n<br />\n5. 戒口<br />\n我無戒口，我個人覺得食熱氣辣野係會爭啲，但我最嚴重個陣係食得清淡到不得了，我覺得食物唔多關我事，反而壓力仲大影響。<br />\n<br />\nSorry 講得太多好長，有咩問題可以問我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw唔好以為生暗瘡已經好慘，有咩慘過同時間同暗瘡+濕疹搏鬥緊，共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803f32683a947e6fb7949c84aefe948482f2557f","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0875838b735bdca308394d11fa51b474c7c7b2","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4c5be7a5404f1834ec331f65a576338edd1ad5","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8807b72ab5cb21b8fabc94fce948f8ae6946cf","tid":2374611,"uid":69157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"結論：武肺少咗返工 少咗壓力 <br />\n所以少咗暗瘡"},{"pid":"d16bc8f8ea41dd1d57b38287b2708eba87f1467a","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a8807b72ab5cb21b8fabc94fce948f8ae6946cf","tid":2374611,"uid":69157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"結論：武肺少咗返工 少咗壓力 <br />\n所以少咗暗瘡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"仲返緊學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但少咗見人少咗化妝係有影響嘅"},{"pid":"33eefe0cfbf67c5ff3dbe903c4ae53174e9e7d20","tid":2374611,"uid":71072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"c打有無去印心得<br />\n前排爆左勁多石頭瘡<br />\n留左好多好深既印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab1ee2c9f6d302f2b1839a0b3f798b64a7f87c0","tid":2374611,"uid":175673,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"想暗瘡好就停化妝，就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"6a0de1eec6bbb463060aa3c5b2023ab5b23c239d","tid":2374611,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"有冇去印心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲印真係好煩"},{"pid":"62d11734e884edb7a0d21bed8487e914e6cb7543","tid":2374611,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"20年天氣乾淨咗好多，呢個我覺得都幾關事，鼻敏感都少咗"},{"pid":"7b63fb4b2a3dbfd801cbf543ebd782dc26f94fc0","tid":2374611,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0cb84b898969f62a384aa24ab14c67542141d86d","tid":2374611,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩戴到兩邊面狂爆，點搞好"},{"pid":"5cdc0cfcbbfc626238457a2475d53f2444c070c6","tid":2374611,"uid":12336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"反而因為戴口罩搞到生多左暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0487e18b56178f475847d8cfaa0bb68260b7fbab","tid":2374611,"uid":66716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"戴到生粒粒喎反而<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2960443eb50711b129fe1091cae13e562e46f1be","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33eefe0cfbf67c5ff3dbe903c4ae53174e9e7d20","tid":2374611,"uid":71072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"c打有無去印心得<br />\n前排爆左勁多石頭瘡<br />\n留左好多好深既印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:16:06.000Z","msg":"我主要係用陶土個隻水敷，佢可以減紅同埋去少少印，如果好返真係得深色印無紅嘅，我會一星期用Cure natural aqua gel 去一次角質，但要盡量避免有暗瘡嘅位。另外唔知係咪我本身好鍾意飲檸水、食奇異果，我啲印係好得快過其他人。仲有我會搽防曬防止佢更深色。"},{"pid":"9b2cd5bea78370eb21206bd0d6c2b57bff9f2216","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb84b898969f62a384aa24ab14c67542141d86d","tid":2374611,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩戴到兩邊面狂爆，點搞好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"你戴口罩之後面有明顯油左？生嘅暗瘡係咩類型？<br />\n我建議你早晚敷我講個兩隻爽膚水，同埋可以用茶樹。面兩頰都可能關護髮素、枕頭套事。"},{"pid":"7af6ce4bed09eb3746e3a05bd9e75535c97e24f3","tid":2374611,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b2cd5bea78370eb21206bd0d6c2b57bff9f2216","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb84b898969f62a384aa24ab14c67542141d86d","tid":2374611,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩戴到兩邊面狂爆，點搞好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"你戴口罩之後面有明顯油左？生嘅暗瘡係咩類型？<br />\n我建議你早晚敷我講個兩隻爽膚水，同埋可以用茶樹。面兩頰都可能關護髮素、枕頭套事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"以前兩邊面好少 自戴口罩開始爆多好多 無停過， 有暗粒，有啲就紅色會痛會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab39fe332376844e1325d4227a4c165919c0e01","tid":2374611,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"我相反帶口罩生多左,但食益生菌又無左7成<br />\n就算生都好快謝,以前無1星期都唔會謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86efe6f58933d4d1598f723d308332a56387f79d","tid":2374611,"uid":343257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a5aefd12a7b7fcfc64fbfc224247b224d67636","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹自大學開始一直受暗瘡困擾，已有數年。自武漢肺炎爆發，美容院關閉，我有大半年無做facial 無做針清，但神奇地生少咗好多暗瘡，之前生襯一爆就額頭+兩頰，而家基本上淨係額頭間中會有，兩頰都冇乜點生。呢半年我都做咗唔少護膚清潔上嘅改變，想整好啲皮膚，以下綜合咗幾樣，我認為係對暗瘡治療有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅皮膚狀態：T字位會比較多油，生嘅暗瘡有時石頭瘡，但大部分都係生啲有癑，細細粒令人好想唧個種。生來生去都生喺舊個啲位。如果有人同我都係咁，我建議你睇埋落去。<br />\nBtw 我用個啲野全完都勁平，無錢但又想take care 皮膚狀況嘅人都可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好唧佢<br />\n針清、自己用針唧、用棉花棒唧都唔好做，咁樣會令到有好多傷口更易發炎。等到佢熟，洗面嘅時候佢就會自然爆，到時再搽茶樹gel。我諗返之前發現我針清完一個星期係會好啲，但第二個星期就多數會又生返，沒完沒了。<br />\n<br />\n2. 用咩清潔<br />\n唔化妝時就早晚用清水清潔。化咗妝要落妝，為咗要確保乾淨，我眼嘴個啲位會用Bioderma 粉紅色卸妝水，面就會用油，大家聽到油可能會好驚，我用緊shu uemura 綠色個隻洗完好乾淨乾爽就唔會lup痴痴。沖完涼之後，我會用innisfree 綠色個隻洗面，洗面嗰陣盡量細力啲，最後過水用按壓嘅方法，減少對皮膚嘅刺激，正常洗完面塊面唔應該紅。<br />\n<br />\n3. 用咩搽暗瘡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQVdwDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQVdwDG.png&h=c443de65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搽嘅時候記得，記得，記得，每搽一粒暗瘡都要用新一邊嘅棉花棒，唔好搽完一粒又一粒。呢枝野勁平，好似30蚊一枝。gel又勁清爽，個人感覺佢幾好。<br />\n<br />\n4. 用咩護膚品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yqdwD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yqdwD3.png&h=7ddf3e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKfQySo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKfQySo.png&h=1c6540de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爽膚水我仲會用薏仁爽膚水，好平勁大枝，洗完面就倒落化妝棉成塊面敷五分鐘。個枝陶土就淨係敷喺暗瘡上面。保濕我都係亂咁揀，保濕就好了<br />\n<br />\n5. 戒口<br />\n我無戒口，我個人覺得食熱氣辣野係會爭啲，但我最嚴重個陣係食得清淡到不得了，我覺得食物唔多關我事，反而壓力仲大影響。<br />\n<br />\nSorry 講得太多好長，有咩問題可以問我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw唔好以為生暗瘡已經好慘，有咩慘過同時間同暗瘡+濕疹搏鬥緊，共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"我重慘過你<br />\n因為我暗瘡濕疹之餘仲要脫髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申20歲"},{"pid":"ec45d1f0fc7c8e45871df58b420bbdb2576770b4","tid":2374611,"uid":106879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2991af51f1e8e325384e96067e4b968947bbe31d","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86efe6f58933d4d1598f723d308332a56387f79d","tid":2374611,"uid":343257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a5aefd12a7b7fcfc64fbfc224247b224d67636","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s