faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw唔好以為生暗瘡已經好慘，有咩慘過同時間同暗瘡+濕疹搏鬥緊，共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"我重慘過你<br />\n因為我暗瘡濕疹之餘仲要脫髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申20歲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都喺咁甩頭髮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"上年之前都只係濕疹<br />\n今年反而唔知jm9生埋暗瘡加脫髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問你有冇用a酸？"},{"pid":"02bb66b4c295f0a39da61e7c2c00e6f665d3e087","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789baa2cd012d2b0006ef9beaa0a03a10bbec9c0","tid":2374611,"uid":343257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2991af51f1e8e325384e96067e4b968947bbe31d","tid":2374611,"uid":171902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86efe6f58933d4d1598f723d308332a56387f79d","tid":2374611,"uid":343257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"我重慘過你<br />\n因為我暗瘡濕疹之餘仲要脫髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申20歲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都喺咁甩頭髮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"上年之前都只係濕疹<br />\n今年反而唔知jm9生埋暗瘡加脫髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問你有冇用a酸？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有食